    dc:description "FIGURE 26. Anguillicola crassus Kuwahara, Niimi & Itagaki, 1974. A. female, buccal capsule; B. male, anterior end; C. female, tail; D. male, tail with five rather than the usual six caudal papillae; E. vulva; F. egg containing 2 nd - stage larva. (Redrawn from Moravec 2013)" ;
